# ── Legend ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
legend: |md
  **Signal Flow Legend**
  → Animated red: SIGINT delivery path
  → Animated yellow: `-ERESTARTSYS` propagation
  → Green: SA_RESTART transparent restart
  → Orange: SA_RESTART absent → EINTR to userspace
  ╌ Blue dashed: spurious wakeup loop-back
  ✕ Red dashed: BUG paths
| {
  near: bottom-right
  style: {
    fill: "#0d0d1a"
    stroke: "#444466"
    font-color: "#a0a0cc"
    font-size: 11
